===Proverb===
{{cmn-proverb|s|pin=cōngmíng făn bèi cōngmíng wù|pint=cong1ming2fan3bei4cong1ming2wu4|tra=聰明反被聰明誤|sim=聪明反被聪明误|rs=耳09}}
